location.fullValue: Angela Johnston Director Of Sales 10929 Bourbon St #3525E3

data.description: Here is your DREAM HOME Beautiful 4 bedroom, 4.5 bath Custom Built Home on almost a half acre corner lot that is just a short walk to the banks of Lake Conroe. 4242 square feet of livable space that includes 2 primary bedrooms down both with ensuite baths, a dedicated home office and multiple dining and entertaining space . This home is a one of a kind home that has so much to offer; crown molding and beautiful built ins throughout, 3 gas fire places, chef's kitchen that includes a huge island with cooktop as well as vegetable sink and open concept kitchen/breakfast/den. Outdoor space is perfect for summer BBQ’s with the huge patio that’s already plumbed for an outdoor kitchen and can accommodate all your Friends with the extra long double driveway and 2 garage with attached 2 car carport. Designers touch throughout, NEW ROOF 2021 AND LOW HOA DUES. This house is a MUST SEE! Owners hate to leave but are relocating so have priced below appraised value for Quick Sale.
